  <dc:description>An assets/bundle library, inspired by UABE's AssetsTools. Read and write assets and bundle files from engine versions 5.x and later. For most cases, you'll need the class data file which you can find in the AssetRipper/Tpk repo. See the wiki for usage and examples.</dc:description>
  <dc:identifier>AssetsTools.NET</dc:identifier>
